(Existing Internal Route Mapping) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Pilot API | SentinelOS runtime |) Tj
T*
(| --- | --- |) Tj
T*
(| `POST /v1/workflow/init` | `POST /task-templates/ingest` |) Tj
T*
(| `POST /v1/workflow/execute` | `task.template.execute` |) Tj
T*
(| `POST /v1/approvals/resolve` | approval store + approval resolution |) Tj
T*
(| `GET /v1/audit/:runId` | audit stream + execution session lookup |) Tj
T*
(| `POST /v1/telemetry/harmonize` | Governed Telemetry Harmonizer |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Key Principle) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(All actions are executed through governed commands.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Nothing executes, and nothing sensitive is exposed, without policy alignment.) Tj
T*
